## TC-001 — Login with Valid Credentials
Pre-Conditions: Site is reachable
Test Data: standard_user / secret_sauce
Steps:
 1. Navigate to site
 2. Enter valid credentials
 3. Click Login
Expected Result: Login successful → Products page
Actual Result: PASS

## TC-002 — Login with Invalid Credentials
Pre-Conditions: Site is reachable
Test Data: invalid_user / invalid_pass
Steps:
 1. Navigate to site
 2. Enter invalid credentials
 3. Click Login
Expected Result: Error message
Actual Result: PASS

## TC-003 — Add Product to Cart
Steps:
 1. Login
 2. Add any product to cart
 3. Open Cart
Expected Result: Product present in cart
Actual Result: PASS

## TC-004 — Remove Product from Cart
Steps:
 1. Login
 2. Add product to cart
 3. Go to Cart
 4. Remove product
Expected Result: Item removed
Actual Result: PASS

## TC-005 — Checkout
Steps:
 1. Login
 2. Add product
 3. Checkout
Expected Result: Order confirmation message
Actual Result: PASS
